headline: GDT named NetApp's Flash Partner of the Year for FY25
summary: Global IT solutions provider GDT announced today that it has been named the NetApp North America Flash Partner of the Year, recognizing overall flash revenue, significant YoY growth, and strategic account wins in NetApp's fiscal year 2025 (FY'25). The North America Partner Awards winners have exemplified NetApp's goal of being customer-centric and understanding and selling NetApp solutions across its cloud, flash, and NetApp Keystone® portfolios.
